% Scope of this file
%   Foundational and methodological literature that Phase 2 chapters are
%   expected to cite. It is deliberately restricted to work whose
%   existence, title, venue, and identifier are stable and checkable.
%   It contains no benchmark results, no prices, no parameter counts,
%   and no model specifications. Those enter through data/*.csv only.
%
% Rules for this file
%   1. The citation key MUST equal the source_id in data/sources.csv.
%   2. No entry is cited in prose until its matching row exists in
%      data/sources.csv with a confirmed access_date and evidence_grade.
%      scripts/validate_sources.py --check-citations enforces this.
%   3. Author lists are recorded as "First Author and others" at seed
%      time and expanded to the full list at verification, from the
%      published record. Do not expand them from memory.
%   4. Where a peer-reviewed version exists, cite it and keep the
%      preprint identifier in the note field.
%   5. Add a doi field at verification. Prefer DOI links over URLs.
%
% Verification queue: see data-sources.md, section 5.
% =====================================================================


